  "description": "<i>International Football</i> is a management game allowing you to participate in the World Cup with a choice of 32 teams from around the world. With your squad of 20 players you can train the players as well as change your tactics and playing styles. Once you are happy with your selections it is time to play your next game. On the match screen you can see both teams kit but the match is described in text. You can see a timer, the score and any incidents that occur. During a game and at half time you can substitute players or change tactics.",
